		<title>打噴嚏、沒食慾？小心是貓咪感冒了！解析 4 種常見感染徵兆</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/22/%e6%89%93%e5%99%b4%e5%9a%8f%e3%80%81%e6%b2%92%e9%a3%9f%e6%85%be%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e5%bf%83%e6%98%af%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e6%84%9f%e5%86%92%e4%ba%86%ef%bc%81%e8%a7%a3%e6%9e%90-4-%e7%a8%ae%e5%b8%b8/</link>
		
