					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="1707" height="2560" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1707&amp;ssl=1 1707w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1365%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1365w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=97%2C146&amp;ssl=1 97w" sizes="(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 最近有名飼主在網路上分享自家狗狗與貓咪的有趣互動引起網上熱議，一隻哈士奇與兩隻 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/21/%e8%b6%85%e9%bb%8f%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%9a%84%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9%e8%b6%b4%e5%9c%a8%e5%93%88%e5%a3%ab%e5%a5%87%e9%a0%ad%e4%b8%8a%e8%ae%93%e7%89%a0%e7%94%9f/">超黏狗狗的貓咪？小貓整天趴在哈士奇頭上讓牠生無可戀 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="1707" height="2560" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=1707&amp;ssl=1 1707w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1024%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1365%2C2048&amp;ssl=1 1365w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/thomas-de-fretes-OOUlnUvZniU-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=97%2C146&amp;ssl=1 97w" sizes="(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>最近有名飼主在網路上分享自家狗狗與貓咪的有趣互動引起網上熱議，一隻哈士奇與兩隻貓咪共同生活在一個家庭，但二哈不知道有什麼魔力，竟然讓小貓們整天都黏在牠的身上，甚至還有隻貓咪頻頻想要把頭塞進哈士奇的耳朵裡探索，讓狗狗經常露出生無可戀的表情，仿佛早已放棄治療。&nbsp;</p>



<p>這名飼主在家裡分別養了一隻哈士奇與兩隻貓咪，狗狗的名字叫做「小雪」，是家中最大的姐姐，另外兩隻貓咪則分別叫做「 Chibi 」與「 Mike 」，牠們平時就很喜歡和「小雪」互動，早已經把對方當成是自己心目中最重要的家人。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="813" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C813&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-229798" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/road-ahead-gGU3lanpKAs-unsplash-1-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">原來「 Chibi 」與「 Mike 」當初被領養回家時，是「小雪」將牠們一手照顧到大<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>這天「小雪」正在客廳的地板上躺著休息時，「&nbsp;Chibi 」與「 Mike 」如往常般地靠近，前者將自己的頭部死死貼住狗狗的耳朵，就像是想一頭鑽進「小雪」的耳朵內部幫忙做清潔服務一般，後者則是將自己的頭與手靠在狗狗的嘴巴旁邊，安穩的熟睡緩緩進入夢鄉，畫面相當逗趣又溫馨。&nbsp;</p>



<p>「小雪」與兩隻貓咪的獨特相處模式引起網友熱烈討論，許多飼主也分享自家狗狗與貓咪的互動日常，讓不少人紛紛留言表示「小雪脾氣真好」、「耳朵到底有什麼魔力」、「令類的溫馨日常」、「大姊姊風範」、「也太無奈哈哈」。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/21/%e8%b6%85%e9%bb%8f%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%9a%84%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%ef%bc%9f%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e6%95%b4%e5%a4%a9%e8%b6%b4%e5%9c%a8%e5%93%88%e5%a3%ab%e5%a5%87%e9%a0%ad%e4%b8%8a%e8%ae%93%e7%89%a0%e7%94%9f/">超黏狗狗的貓咪？小貓整天趴在哈士奇頭上讓牠生無可戀 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
