					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1698" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1019&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1358&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=220%2C146&amp;ssl=1 220w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 近日網路上有段充滿療癒感的街頭畫面，一隻忠心陪伴主人的狗狗，在擺攤賣菜的過程中 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/21/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8a%e7%8f%ad%ef%bc%9f%e5%8f%af%e6%84%9b%e5%b0%8f%e7%8b%97%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e7%bd%b7%e5%b7%a5%e7%9d%a1%e6%ad%bb%e7%95%ab%e9%9d%a2%e8%b6%85%e7%99%82%e7%99%92/">最平凡的幸福！狗狗每日陪著主人上班溫馨互動惹哭全網</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1698" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1019&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1358&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=220%2C146&amp;ssl=1 220w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/khanh-do-0OkStSFHxeY-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>近日網路上有段充滿療癒感的街頭畫面，一隻忠心陪伴主人的狗狗，在擺攤賣菜的過程中忍不住犯睏，直接躺倒在地、閉眼進入夢鄉，這溫馨又可愛的瞬間不只融化現場氣氛，也讓無數網友直呼「太療癒了！」。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這隻狗狗的名字叫做「多多」，是一位阿嬤從小照顧長大的，「多多」的性格親人愛撒嬌，經常黏在主人身邊，每天早上都會跟著阿嬤一起到街頭擺攤販售蔬菜，直到下午收攤時才會跟著一起回家。</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="691" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C691&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-229799" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C435&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C869&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1159&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=390%2C220&amp;ssl=1 390w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=258%2C146&amp;ssl=1 258w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/bacon3floors-CmtzPK7jcEM-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">「多多」與阿嬤的互動只是再平凡不過的日常，也是最幸福的陪伴<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>這天阿嬤一如既往地在街頭擺攤，「多多」也乖巧地待在一旁陪伴，但隨著時間過去，狗狗逐漸支撐不住睡意，最後竟一屁股坐下、慢慢躺平，直接進入熟睡狀態，對此阿嬤反而露出欣慰的笑容，還忍不住伸手輕撫愛犬，畫面令人動容。&nbsp;</p>



<p>「多多」與主人的互動雖然對於牠們而言只是再平凡不過的日常，卻展現出濃濃的人寵情誼，狗狗始終在阿嬤的身旁默默守候，主人也以溫柔回應，讓這段沒有言語卻顯露出深厚感情的真摯互動格外溫暖，也再度證明幸福其實就藏在最平凡的陪伴裡。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/21/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e6%83%b3%e4%b8%8a%e7%8f%ad%ef%bc%9f%e5%8f%af%e6%84%9b%e5%b0%8f%e7%8b%97%e7%9b%b4%e6%8e%a5%e7%bd%b7%e5%b7%a5%e7%9d%a1%e6%ad%bb%e7%95%ab%e9%9d%a2%e8%b6%85%e7%99%82%e7%99%92/">最平凡的幸福！狗狗每日陪著主人上班溫馨互動惹哭全網</a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
